{"type": "article", "id": 38618, "title": "布满小点的智能手表，想让盲人摸出讯息｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-03-09T23:24:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 38384, "name": "Classic Engineering"}, {"id": 38385, "name": "Blaha office"}, {"id": 38386, "name": "Brigitta Nemeth"}, {"id": 38387, "name": "Moisés Hernández"}, {"id": 38388, "name": "Zoe Wetherall"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 165, "image": "img/article/article_show/201703092141318mUrchiKfP4Iv1eG.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>DOT</h3><p>尽管市面上有不少智能手机为视障人士加入了辅助功能，智能手表领域的革新却比较罕见。为了填补这一空缺，来自韩国的初创公司 <a href=\"https://dotincorp.com/\">DOT</a> 历时三年时间，研发出了世界上第一款盲文智能手表。和常见智能表面不同，DOT 的触控屏上有 24 个小点，通过上下浮动的形式展现盲文的变化。与手机配对后，讯息都会翻译成盲文发送给 DOT 并以震动提醒用户。除了基本的功能之外，公司还开放了 DOT 的 API，欢迎其他开发者为它加入更多便捷的功能。DOT 的定价在 300 美元左右，预计于 4 月 1 日正式交付。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214222idl8WteXcTLHo5xj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214222tljhRCUrieV1Q68A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562696\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214224uWx2oJqivgwZ4VA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.976136\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214225nqpvF2r0QbaijOL3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Classic Möbius by Classic Engineering</h3><p>哥伦比亚设计师 Eduardo Umaña 带来的 <a href=\"http://classic.engineering/introducing-classic-mobius\">Classic Möbius</a> 是一款在造型上借鉴了莫比乌斯环的智能灯饰。灯条由陶土等复合材料制成，烧制后围绕着软木制成的灯柱扭曲、旋转，内部各镶嵌了一条 4000K 的 LED 灯带。除了外观，Classic Möbius 的科技加持也相当抢眼：软木灯柱内置了数字麦克风和传感器，只要吹一声口哨就能控制它的开关。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214240Z2pJqmhT54O6cNrD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214239bKfCT7SkNLOP0wMj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250617\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214239FBHJ8O13ptbxwK7s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>PAIS by Brigitta Nemeth</h3><p>为了让在开放环境下工作的办公族也能享有属于自己的一席之地，匈牙利设计师 <a href=\"http://brigittanemeth.com/\">Brigitta Nemeth</a> 为家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.blaha.co.at/\">Blaha office</a> 打造了一款名为 PAIS 的桌面屏风。PAIS 可以通过配套的金属条吸附在任何办公桌的边缘，在不需要的时候还能变成一张不规则的吸音板或是装饰壁贴，无论是收纳还是摊开都很灵活便捷。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214329bZNMLgd4s1VFC7iB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.539773\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214328L1K9mueaFVbDXTUO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.539773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214329GlAVRvE4LJkOX3wq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.539773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214330mxqXzd2Kk6s8beoy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.539773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214330O9vJ8wiPuQTnZ1ey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Immersed birds by Moisés Hernández</h3><p>巨嘴鸟、蜂鸟、绿咬鹃，这三种有着鲜艳羽毛的热带鸟类在墨西哥设计师 <a href=\"http://www.moises-hernandez.com/\">Moisés Hernández</a> 推出的木雕系列 Immersed Birds 中不再以尖锐的艳丽感夺人眼球，多了一种圆润可爱的气质。为模仿羽毛的颜色，Hernández 采用了实验性的手工浸泡法，以浸入有色水的角度和时长决定颜色的深浅和覆盖区域。在保留天然木纹的同时，这种灵活的上色技巧成功为鸟儿们穿上了通透的渐变色“新衣”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214310WQtzFT54xKeh7syV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214311ODxLbX6KC3qlM0QW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214310ZrDzalo1ETt8LyW0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214311vAc4K9oWNblGdthH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214311aPXNdDHfl0vq2Crt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.273266\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214311H4ktUf9YFW5TvpZw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.970812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Order by Zoe Wetherall</h3><p>生活在大城市的你有没有留心过建筑表面有规律的不断重复的图案？现居纽约的澳大利亚摄影师 <a href=\"http://zoewetherall.com/\">Zoe Wetherall</a> 最近公开了一组名为 <a href=\"http://blog.zoewetherall.com/order/\">Order</a> 的作品，这些抽象的图案其实都是她在各地游历时所捕捉到的楼宇中的细节，她希望通过这种类似放大镜的呈现方式让更多人发现当代建筑的精确和秩序美。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214258eHhWyorOmKPx2j7C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214258Y1QvbeZzIyxPFATg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214259YyMqUzFcoutJlhLO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214259D5OaY4FNzcBxPLbM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214258vwrbY2a0jld5unxN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214300sADTz207vw5BQFqm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Food carvings by Gaku</h3><p>同样是食雕，日本艺术家 Gaku 更喜欢在食材表面下功夫：将蔬果对半切开之后，他就开始同时间赛跑，力求在氧化变色前在表面留下传统的日式花纹。如果你喜欢这类作品，还可以关注 Gaku 的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gakugakugakugakugaku1/\">Instagram</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214504HQ7eDmjIKfdAi1yv.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214505EajoAkMF2Cv5Zlwg.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.160000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214505ZuqDiI9Erv5dSjcF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214506jP6c2H7Mqyx89EBr.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.870605\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170309214506zgye4xhnWwjN2bTQ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552469\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703092145073aZbBPgeI6qJcxAN.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748596\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}